### =============================================================================
### ✅ SUPER ADMIN LOGIN
### =============================================================================

### [1] Valid credentials — expect 200 + tokens
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/super-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "karananimesh144@gmail.com",
  "password": "Karan@144#"
}

###

### [2] Wrong password — expect 401 + AuditLog row with WRONG_PASSWORD
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/super-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "karananimesh144@gmail.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### [3] Email not found — expect 401 + AuditLog row with EMAIL_NOT_FOUND
### Response time should be same as [2] — timing attack protection
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/super-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "doesnotexist@test.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

